meaning_str.bing:
n. 下巴；颏
v. 〈口〉用下巴夹住(提琴等)；(单杠)引体向上使下巴高过横杠；谈话
网络. 镇元斋；下颚；秦

〈口〉用下巴夹住(提琴等)；(单杠)引体向上使下巴高过横杠；谈话

下巴；颏；（一次）引体向上动作；聊天；闲谈
在（单杠等上）作引体向上动作；将（小提琴）放在颏下；<俚>聊天；闲谈；<非正式>击打下巴

1.en: You take the lid, put your arm through the hole, take hold of my chin and pull it up high enough to put the lid on.
1.cn: 你采取盖子，把你的手臂，透过洞，把握我的下巴和拉起来不够高，把盖子上。

2.en: Nor did she all herself to hold her head at an angle, or to let it fall, or to lean her chin on her hand.
2.cn: 她也不歪着头，也不地下头，或者把下巴捂在手里。

3.en: Her lips and chin had a gentle firmness, and in her pale green suit she was like springtime come alive.
3.cn: 她的嘴唇和下巴有一个温柔的坚定，她身穿淡绿色套装，就好像春天一样。

0.en: You know, when she tells "The Three Little Pigs" story, she actually has hair on her chinny chin chin.
0.cn: 当然，当她讲“三只小猪”的故事时，她的下巴上是真的有胡子的。

1.en: Last week when you found those two chin hairs, you weren't so chipper.
1.cn: 上周你发现下巴长了两根毛时，可没这么开心。

2.en: Yeah, but it was 1982, and my Flock of Seagulls haircut was tickling her chin.
2.cn: 有啊，不过那是1982年，我的海鸥发型让她的下巴发痒。

3.en: I don't think so at all. Your chin is very nice, very nice. Your mom sounds insane.
3.cn: 我一点没觉得，你的下巴很漂亮，很漂亮，你妈疯了吧。

4.en: Do you expect me to build this? I expect you to wipe the pudding off your chin. Gentlemen.
4.cn: 你是想我帮你造出来吗？我是想你擦擦嘴角的布丁，大家再见。

5.en: My guy is a lawyer who has volunteer work. And, he has one of these. A face ass? A chin dimple.
5.cn: 我这个是律师，还当义工，而且他有这个东西。脸屁股？下巴窝啦。

6.en: It's like when I started doing chin-ups. I didn't want you to see until I could do one. FYI, really close.
6.cn: 这像我开始练引体向上时，做不到一个前，我都没脸让你看，顺便说一声，差点就成功了。

7.en: Do you realize that teaching is the first thing I've failed at since my ill-fated attempt to complete a chin-up in March of 1989?
7.cn: 你知不知道，教书是我自从1989年3月做引体向上失败以后搞砸的第一件事。

8.en: Maybe it means something. I doubt it. Yeah. I don't think so. Where's my car? You've got to put that thing to your chin. This? Yeah.
8.cn: 或许这意味着些什么。是吗。是啊，或许是的。我车呢？把那个放在你下巴那。这个？是的。

9.en: My parents like to criticize me too. When I was growing up, my mom said that I had a really big chin. And that's why guys wouldn't like me.
9.cn: 我爸妈也爱挑我毛病，小时候我妈说我下巴很大，所以男生都不喜欢我。
